WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.710
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.230 --> 02:50.000
[Episode 10]

02:51.520 --> 02:52.560
Oh, right.

02:52.560 --> 02:54.150
You're a Kunlun disciple.

02:54.570 --> 02:55.660
Tell us.

02:55.690 --> 02:56.690
What happened

02:56.750 --> 02:57.960
1000 years ago?

02:59.530 --> 03:01.020
A thousand years ago...

03:02.490 --> 03:03.450
It was a tragedy.

03:03.480 --> 03:04.530
Get to the point.

03:06.130 --> 03:07.120
Back then,

03:07.140 --> 03:08.980
Ling Long, the Saintess of the Fox Clan, entered Kunlun

03:09.480 --> 03:10.950
and fell in love with Rong Xian, the Saint.

03:10.970 --> 03:13.640
But their love was not accepted by either clan.

03:13.670 --> 03:16.170
Eventually, they lived in seclusion, away from the world.

03:16.220 --> 03:17.290
Yet, for some unknown reason,

03:17.310 --> 03:18.160
one day,

03:18.190 --> 03:20.070
Ling Long suddenly attacked Kunlun

03:20.090 --> 03:21.530
and slaughtered the entire clan.

03:23.320 --> 03:25.280
Mr. Rong Xian, upon hearing the news, rushed back.

03:25.300 --> 03:26.870
Not only did he kill Ling Long,

03:26.900 --> 03:28.980
but he also went on a killing spree in Jingyou Mountain

03:29.020 --> 03:30.220
and avenged

03:30.250 --> 03:31.090
Kunlun.

03:37.520 --> 03:39.280
But Ling Long

03:39.380 --> 03:41.560
doesn't seem to be such a cruel person.

03:41.960 --> 03:43.240
Why did she slaughter Kunlun?

03:43.579 --> 03:44.630
I don't know either.

03:45.870 --> 03:47.680
But there's one thing I've heard about.

03:47.710 --> 03:49.120
When Ling Long entered Kunlun back then,

03:49.120 --> 03:50.100
she brought three people with her.

03:50.120 --> 03:51.120
One was her younger sister,

03:51.190 --> 03:52.079
and the other two were her attendants.

03:55.160 --> 03:56.600
Isn't that us three?

03:57.810 --> 03:59.160
Stop stating the obvious.

03:59.810 --> 04:00.760
Since this place

04:00.790 --> 04:02.210
is formed from Rong Xian's resentment,

04:02.250 --> 04:03.970
if we kill him in this illusion,

04:04.000 --> 04:05.370
will the resentment disappear?

04:06.230 --> 04:07.390
No.

04:07.760 --> 04:10.250
Kunlun Illusion is tied to the caster's life.

04:10.280 --> 04:11.110
If you kill him,

04:11.130 --> 04:12.700
you'll only kill the version of him in the illusion.

04:12.720 --> 04:14.000
The illusion won't be destroyed,

04:14.030 --> 04:15.430
and instead, we'll be trapped here forever.

04:18.440 --> 04:20.019
There might be a way out.

04:20.920 --> 04:23.530
If the illusion is formed from Rong Xian's resentment,

04:23.550 --> 04:25.910
then if we can stop Ling Long from slaughtering Kunlun,

04:25.940 --> 04:27.580
we might be able to quell his resentment

04:27.600 --> 04:28.500
and break the illusion.

04:29.280 --> 04:30.630
That makes sense.

04:30.650 --> 04:31.620
So, what...

04:31.650 --> 04:32.640
should we do now?

04:33.460 --> 04:36.050
All we need to do is one thing:

04:36.100 --> 04:38.110
stop Ling Long and Rong Xian from falling in love with each other.

04:39.720 --> 04:40.610
Wu.

04:43.940 --> 04:46.180
Why are you two acting so strange today?

04:46.210 --> 04:48.770
Aren't you usually inseparable?

04:48.790 --> 04:49.620
What happened?

04:49.650 --> 04:50.800
Have you two suddenly become distant?

04:53.610 --> 04:54.970
How is that possible?

04:55.110 --> 04:56.380
They are very close.

04:56.400 --> 04:57.530
-Right?
-Yes.

04:57.790 --> 04:58.650
You three

04:58.680 --> 05:00.210
must protect each other

05:00.230 --> 05:01.240
and prioritize the overall picture.

05:01.840 --> 05:03.570
Now Rong Xian wants to see us.

05:03.600 --> 05:04.360
Remember,

05:04.400 --> 05:05.960
he is the guardian of the Snow Lotus.

05:05.980 --> 05:07.830
We must follow the plan and gain his trust.

05:17.280 --> 05:18.920
What exactly is the Fox Clan's plan?

05:19.660 --> 05:20.910
The beauty trap.

05:23.590 --> 05:25.180
Who will be the beauty?

05:25.200 --> 05:26.160
You?

05:28.710 --> 05:29.800
Me?

05:34.010 --> 05:35.060
Saintess,

05:35.090 --> 05:35.850
please.

05:38.370 --> 05:40.250
Please.

05:42.640 --> 05:43.640
This young lady

05:43.659 --> 05:44.990
is quite different.

05:45.480 --> 05:46.970
Saint, please excuse us.

05:47.000 --> 05:48.360
This is my younger sister, Wu.

05:48.380 --> 05:50.140
It's our fault for spoiling her so much

05:50.170 --> 05:51.680
that she lacks proper manners.

05:51.950 --> 05:53.850
Let me toast to you on her behalf.

06:01.520 --> 06:03.080
Saintess, you are unconventional and poised.

06:03.100 --> 06:05.360
You're quite different from what I imagined

06:05.380 --> 06:06.450
a Fox Clan girl to be like.

06:06.480 --> 06:07.720
How?

06:07.740 --> 06:09.940
The world believes the Fox Clan to be petty,

06:09.970 --> 06:11.110
always haggling over every penny.

06:11.140 --> 06:12.310
But seeing you today,

06:12.330 --> 06:14.970
I feel the world has misunderstood the Fox Clan.

06:15.000 --> 06:15.750
Both of you

06:16.290 --> 06:17.930
are truly generous people.

06:17.960 --> 06:19.800
Kunlun is a righteous sect,

06:19.820 --> 06:21.050
open-minded and inclusive.

06:21.520 --> 06:22.910
You have a sharp eye,

06:22.930 --> 06:25.660
unlike those shallow and ignorant people.

06:25.680 --> 06:26.680
I toast to you

06:26.740 --> 06:28.590
in admiration of your noble character

06:28.610 --> 06:29.960
and trust in my clan.

06:33.750 --> 06:34.780
Oh no.

06:34.860 --> 06:36.570
As the toasts keep coming,

06:36.590 --> 06:38.240
it feels like they really hit it off.

06:38.980 --> 06:39.740
Saint!

06:46.360 --> 06:47.180
Saint,

06:47.720 --> 06:50.320
my apologies for earlier.

06:50.340 --> 06:52.070
I like divination.

06:52.100 --> 06:54.110
How about I offer you a reading

06:54.140 --> 06:55.500
as a greeting today?

06:55.520 --> 06:56.370
That sounds wonderful.

06:56.400 --> 06:58.280
Please, Miss Wu.

07:01.850 --> 07:03.770
This divination technique is quite accurate.

07:03.790 --> 07:05.910
It's called Grain Divination.

07:05.940 --> 07:07.620
If there's anything you want to know,

07:07.640 --> 07:08.520
feel free to ask.

07:08.550 --> 07:10.630
I'll make sure to give you a clear

07:10.650 --> 07:11.390
and correct answer.

07:11.410 --> 07:12.170
Really?

07:12.200 --> 07:13.090
Of course.

07:16.860 --> 07:17.930
In that case,

07:17.950 --> 07:20.070
I'd like to ask you to see

07:20.100 --> 07:21.520
if we are destined to be together.

07:35.050 --> 07:36.150
What?

07:36.180 --> 07:37.270
Are you saying we're in that Rong Xian's

07:37.270 --> 07:38.270
resentment illusion?

07:38.270 --> 07:39.680
Keep your voice down.

07:39.680 --> 07:40.490
Let go of me!

07:40.510 --> 07:42.680
I didn't expect you to be sucked into this realm of resentment too.

07:42.710 --> 07:44.470
Why did you, the Young Master of the Fox Clan,

07:44.490 --> 07:46.710
act so sneaky in participating in the Wutong Martial Arts Contest?

07:46.880 --> 07:47.950
I didn't!

07:49.000 --> 07:51.140
If it weren't for my aunt forbidding me from coming to Outlanders' City,

07:51.210 --> 07:52.850
I wouldn't have had to be so sneaky.

07:52.870 --> 07:54.110
Look what happened now.

07:54.140 --> 07:55.460
I ended up in this stupid illusion

07:55.480 --> 07:56.550
and became a stupid Eternal.

07:56.580 --> 07:57.500
What did you say?

07:57.520 --> 07:58.120
Our Kunlun Sect

07:58.120 --> 07:59.040
is the leader of the...

08:00.000 --> 08:00.390
sword sects,

08:00.420 --> 08:02.300
shining in glory. We're not some stupid Eternals.

08:02.770 --> 08:03.650
Shut up.

08:07.080 --> 08:08.110
Aren't they...

08:08.130 --> 08:09.250
hosting the foxes?

08:09.740 --> 08:11.050
Why didn't you go in?

08:11.220 --> 08:12.900
Master and I are just attendants right now.

08:12.930 --> 08:14.400
We can't sit at the same table as the Saint.

08:18.460 --> 08:20.110
I didn't expect

08:20.260 --> 08:21.700
Master of Bright Moon

08:21.850 --> 08:23.610
to ever be in a position where he couldn't sit at the table.

08:28.760 --> 08:30.670
My aunt is Chang Mei, the Master of Jingyou.

08:30.690 --> 08:32.000
She is one of the three kings.

08:32.450 --> 08:33.659
You can't hit me.

08:33.690 --> 08:34.890
You think

08:34.919 --> 08:36.320
I'm afraid of her?

08:39.630 --> 08:41.030
It's the realm of resentment.

08:57.240 --> 08:57.850
You...

08:58.230 --> 08:59.750
You are Saintess Ling Long?

08:59.770 --> 09:00.650
I've heard a lot about you.

09:00.680 --> 09:02.580
You really are

09:03.060 --> 09:03.960
gorgeous in person.

09:05.190 --> 09:06.530
You are quite interesting.

09:06.930 --> 09:08.290
The Divinity of Kunlun

09:08.310 --> 09:10.090
has heard a lot about the Fox Clan Saintess?

09:10.650 --> 09:12.250
Aren't you afraid of being punished by your sect?

09:15.870 --> 09:18.210
Anyway, I've heard a lot about you.

09:19.590 --> 09:20.630
Where is she?

09:20.720 --> 09:22.130
How are you speaking to the Saintess?

09:22.160 --> 09:23.250
Watch your attitude.

09:26.800 --> 09:28.280
Don't disturb them.

09:28.300 --> 09:29.940
The atmosphere inside is quite harmonious.

09:29.970 --> 09:32.220
It seems Rong Xian has fallen for Wu at first sight.

09:32.250 --> 09:32.900
How about this?

09:32.920 --> 09:34.960
Tonight, let Wu hold off Rong Xian,

09:34.990 --> 09:36.730
and I'll steal the Snow Lotus.

09:38.580 --> 09:39.750
What are you doing?

09:44.730 --> 09:46.440
According to your divination,

09:46.470 --> 09:48.640
I find that we share similar interests.

09:49.170 --> 09:50.810
It's fate.

09:50.890 --> 09:51.480
I'd like

09:51.500 --> 09:53.130
to ask you to read my fortune again.

09:53.150 --> 09:53.980
Would you

09:54.010 --> 09:54.890
like it?

09:54.910 --> 09:56.270
What else do you want to know?

09:56.710 --> 09:58.510
My fate with a girl.

09:58.530 --> 09:59.490
A girl?

10:00.180 --> 10:00.980
Who is it?

10:01.460 --> 10:02.250
Someone...

10:03.520 --> 10:05.240
Someone I've known for a long time.

10:06.140 --> 10:07.820
Known for a long time?

10:07.850 --> 10:09.210
Then it shouldn't be Ling Long.

10:09.820 --> 10:11.210
This Rong Xian.

10:11.240 --> 10:12.880
First, he wanted to know his fate with me,

10:12.900 --> 10:15.020
then his fate with another woman,

10:15.050 --> 10:17.160
and later, he'll fall in love with Ling Long.

10:17.180 --> 10:19.000
He seems to be a weak-willed,

10:19.020 --> 10:20.810
easily enamored playboy.

10:21.430 --> 10:22.430
But that's good.

10:22.460 --> 10:23.530
The more he behaves like this,

10:23.560 --> 10:25.280
the easier it will be for us to break him and Ling Long up

10:25.300 --> 10:27.400
and prevent the future tragedy.

10:27.850 --> 10:29.490
Then tell me,

10:29.510 --> 10:31.460
when is her birthday?

10:35.800 --> 10:37.810
Her birthday is...

10:37.830 --> 10:38.470
Wu!

10:42.430 --> 10:43.510
Where did this rude servant

10:43.610 --> 10:45.030
come from?

10:46.860 --> 10:47.490
I, the Master...

10:55.680 --> 10:57.730
Is this how people from Kunlun behave,

10:57.750 --> 10:59.150
showing such a lack of courtesy to someone they've just met?

10:59.170 --> 10:59.840
Qi,

11:00.390 --> 11:01.340
don't be rude.

11:02.220 --> 11:03.550
Saint, please forgive us.

11:03.680 --> 11:05.110
This servant of Wu

11:05.130 --> 11:05.610
is...

11:05.640 --> 11:07.090
a bit slow-witted.

11:07.110 --> 11:08.540
He only knows to protect his master,

11:08.570 --> 11:09.750
which is why he offended you.

11:09.780 --> 11:12.350
I'll take him back now and teach him proper manners.

11:12.380 --> 11:13.020
It doesn't matter.

11:13.820 --> 11:14.870
Let's go.

11:18.930 --> 11:20.440
After all these years,

11:21.070 --> 11:22.520
she's still the same.

11:29.330 --> 11:30.960
The Master of Bright Moon fell into the illusion

11:30.990 --> 11:32.630
to save Ms. Bai.

11:32.660 --> 11:34.600
Although the Saint is a true gentleman,

11:34.620 --> 11:36.440
their being alone together

11:36.460 --> 11:37.750
would inevitably make Master suspicious

11:37.750 --> 11:38.770
that Ms. Bai is in danger.

11:38.790 --> 11:40.000
With his temper,

11:40.030 --> 11:41.300
he might cause trouble.

11:42.330 --> 11:43.610
Get it straight.

11:43.630 --> 11:45.110
You are a servant from the Fox Clan now.

11:45.640 --> 11:46.850
If you go in there and stop Fan Yue,

11:46.880 --> 11:48.370
aren't you helping the outsiders?

11:49.060 --> 11:49.910
All you do is make trouble.

11:50.460 --> 11:51.880
Me?

11:52.230 --> 11:54.070
f it weren't for you causing trouble at the Yi Clan Tomb,

11:54.100 --> 11:55.650
we wouldn't have entered this realm of resentment.

11:56.180 --> 11:58.230
Are Kunlun disciples really this vengeful?

11:58.260 --> 11:59.370
Does the Fox Clan

11:59.390 --> 12:00.750
never admit their mistakes?

12:00.780 --> 12:02.350
Rong Xian almost wiped out the Fox Clan.

12:02.370 --> 12:03.890
How is it wrong for me to kill him for revenge?

12:03.920 --> 12:06.000
It was your Saintess who almost wiped out Kunlun.

12:06.020 --> 12:06.850
-Don't make a move.
-I'm going to punch you.

12:06.880 --> 12:08.080
It's the realm of resentment.

12:08.550 --> 12:10.040
-What are you doing? Let me go!
-Let's go.

12:10.280 --> 12:11.810
-Let go of me!
-What are you doing?

12:11.840 --> 12:12.710
The Elder wants to interrogate him.

12:12.730 --> 12:13.670
Follow up.

12:14.420 --> 12:15.530
Interrogate him?

12:20.600 --> 12:22.210
I've already figured it out.

12:23.070 --> 12:24.630
Stop pretending.

12:25.090 --> 12:25.890
Could it be that…

12:25.920 --> 12:28.000
she has figured out we're impostors?

12:28.470 --> 12:29.430
Qi,

12:30.310 --> 12:31.540
you little brat.

12:32.170 --> 12:34.010
You and Wu have been keeping this well from me.

12:34.790 --> 12:35.510
Tell me.

12:36.480 --> 12:37.820
When did you two

12:38.630 --> 12:41.040
start liking each other?

12:44.230 --> 12:45.200
Sister,

12:45.220 --> 12:47.100
it's not what you think.

12:47.130 --> 12:47.850
Wu,

12:47.870 --> 12:48.870
stop explaining.

12:48.900 --> 12:50.910
I've lived for more than 100 years. How could I not see this?

12:50.930 --> 12:53.210
Just now, when Qi heard that Rong Xian was interested in you,

12:53.240 --> 12:55.000
he rushed right in without a second thought.

12:55.020 --> 12:56.530
Even a fool can tell

12:56.560 --> 12:58.010
he cares about you a lot.

12:58.420 --> 13:00.290
He even dared to challenge the Kunlun Saint for you.

13:00.790 --> 13:01.790
Such a fiery spirit.

13:01.810 --> 13:03.520
I've underestimated you all this time.

13:03.710 --> 13:04.430
Young Chief,

13:04.460 --> 13:05.070
you misunderstood.

13:05.120 --> 13:06.520
Why are you so shy?

13:06.540 --> 13:08.610
I think Wu quite likes you too.

13:08.640 --> 13:10.570
You almost ruined our plan just now.

13:10.600 --> 13:11.550
But during this whole time,

13:11.570 --> 13:13.260
she didn't criticize you for your reckless actions.

13:13.290 --> 13:14.200
What does it mean?

13:15.410 --> 13:16.920
It means favoritism.

13:17.200 --> 13:18.530
Only someone who likes you

13:18.560 --> 13:20.080
would protect you like that.

13:20.100 --> 13:21.180
Am I right?

13:21.790 --> 13:22.720
Come on.

13:22.740 --> 13:23.530
Sister,

13:23.560 --> 13:24.800
you really misunderstood.

13:24.820 --> 13:26.650
We're not what you think.

13:26.680 --> 13:27.550
Misunderstood?

13:27.570 --> 13:28.710
Then let me ask you,

13:28.820 --> 13:30.540
when you're in danger,

13:30.560 --> 13:32.350
who do you most want to protect?

13:32.380 --> 13:33.740
When you're bored,

13:33.760 --> 13:35.490
who is the first person you think of?

13:35.520 --> 13:36.730
When you're happy,

13:36.750 --> 13:38.810
who do you want to share it with the most?

13:38.840 --> 13:39.870
When you're sad,

13:39.890 --> 13:41.450
who do you want to talk to?

13:43.600 --> 13:45.570
When you truly like someone,

13:45.590 --> 13:47.230
you think of this person all the time.

13:48.290 --> 13:49.520
Aren't you like that for each other?

13:52.590 --> 13:53.350
Of course,

13:53.370 --> 13:54.850
sometimes the person involved might be too confused

13:54.880 --> 13:56.120
to realize it,

13:56.140 --> 13:57.900
but others can see it clearly.

13:58.570 --> 13:59.550
Qi,

13:59.570 --> 14:01.140
although you're just a servant,

14:01.170 --> 14:02.820
our Fox Clan has always been open-minded

14:02.850 --> 14:04.370
when it comes to love.

14:04.850 --> 14:06.480
Since you two are already in love,

14:06.500 --> 14:07.940
I'm happy to support you.

14:08.090 --> 14:08.850
How about this?

14:08.880 --> 14:10.570
I'll carry out the beauty trap myself.

14:10.590 --> 14:12.070
You two go to the back mountain and steal the Snow Lotus.

14:13.570 --> 14:14.610
If she goes,

14:14.630 --> 14:15.750
it'll be terrible.

14:15.780 --> 14:16.590
No!

14:18.010 --> 14:18.960
Sister,

14:18.990 --> 14:20.200
I like Rong Xian.

14:20.220 --> 14:21.100
I'll go.

14:25.030 --> 14:25.750
Alright.

14:25.780 --> 14:27.350
Stop saying things against your will.

14:27.370 --> 14:28.660
I can't sacrifice your happiness

14:28.680 --> 14:29.880
just to complete the mission

14:29.900 --> 14:31.410
and send you to another man.

14:31.440 --> 14:33.030
It's decided.

14:33.060 --> 14:34.630
Tonight, I'll hold off Rong Xian

14:34.650 --> 14:36.620
while you two go to the back mountain and steal the Snow Lotus.

14:36.650 --> 14:37.760
If you manage to get the Snow Lotus

14:37.780 --> 14:38.870
and make a great contribution,

14:38.900 --> 14:41.340
when we return to the Fox Clan, I'll make sure to speak to the Chief

14:41.360 --> 14:42.790
and appoint you as an Elder.

14:42.820 --> 14:43.430
That way,

14:43.450 --> 14:45.060
you'll be worthy of Wu.

14:45.740 --> 14:47.950
Although Rong Xian already has someone he likes,

14:47.970 --> 14:49.930
the Fox Clan's seduction techniques are unmatched.

14:49.960 --> 14:51.800
How can Rong Xian resist?

14:52.070 --> 14:53.210
So, we need to hurry.

14:53.380 --> 14:54.740
The sooner we get the Snow Lotus and complete the mission,

14:54.840 --> 14:56.760
the sooner we can take Ling Long back to the Fox Clan.

14:57.130 --> 14:59.220
The shorter the time Ling Long spends with Rong Xian,

14:59.420 --> 15:00.830
the less likely they are to fall in love.

15:03.430 --> 15:04.880
I'm still here.

15:04.910 --> 15:05.950
Stop being so lovey-dovey.

15:06.080 --> 15:07.340
Let me remind you,

15:07.390 --> 15:08.910
don't let love

15:08.910 --> 15:10.200
ruin our big plan.

15:10.690 --> 15:12.520
Qi and I will go to the back mountain now.

15:12.540 --> 15:13.940
We'll definitely bring the Snow Lotus back.

15:17.270 --> 15:18.460
The conflict between

15:18.480 --> 15:19.920
the Eternals and demons has been ongoing for all this time,

15:19.940 --> 15:21.910
and Kunlun and the Fox Clans have also been at war endlessly.

15:21.930 --> 15:23.000
Your proposal of peace talks this time

15:23.030 --> 15:24.030
is quite strange and suspicious.

15:24.050 --> 15:25.980
Do you really think Kunlun will believe you?

15:26.380 --> 15:26.950
Tell me.

15:26.970 --> 15:28.250
What is your purpose

15:28.280 --> 15:29.720
in entering Kunlun?

15:29.750 --> 15:30.510
El...

15:33.940 --> 15:35.830
We are truly here for peace talks.

15:35.860 --> 15:36.930
You're full of lies!

15:37.320 --> 15:38.080
You,

15:38.100 --> 15:39.490
beat him up!

15:43.430 --> 15:44.070
Yes!

15:51.120 --> 15:52.000
How dare you!

15:52.390 --> 15:54.060
How dare you, fox demon,

15:54.220 --> 15:56.610
play tricks in front of our Elder?

15:57.350 --> 15:58.640
Speak up!

16:00.560 --> 16:01.630
Let me tell you,

16:01.650 --> 16:02.860
don't do anything reckless.

16:02.890 --> 16:03.610
If we can't break the illusion,

16:03.630 --> 16:04.700
none of us will be able to leave.

16:08.200 --> 16:09.380
Just wait.

16:09.400 --> 16:10.560
When I get out...

16:10.910 --> 16:12.320
Then you should wait until we get out first.

16:34.920 --> 16:36.320
I haven't tasted the sweet dew,

16:36.340 --> 16:37.820
but I've already smelled the sacred fragrance.

16:42.940 --> 16:44.490
Saint, you arrived on time.

16:44.890 --> 16:46.060
This is your invitation,

16:46.090 --> 16:47.490
so I naturally couldn't be late.

16:49.230 --> 16:50.500
If I'm not mistaken,

16:50.520 --> 16:51.970
this tea smells like

16:52.000 --> 16:53.600
the Fox Clan's Nine-Color Flower Tea.

16:53.620 --> 16:55.730
You sure know a lot about the Fox Clan.

16:56.540 --> 16:57.380
That's right.

16:57.410 --> 16:58.650
Nine-Color Flower Tea

16:58.670 --> 17:00.070
has a delicate and refreshing fragrance,

17:00.100 --> 17:03.020
best brewed with water derived from thousand-year-old ice.

17:03.050 --> 17:04.500
I specially brought some

17:04.520 --> 17:06.000
to share with you.

17:06.030 --> 17:07.339
The thousand-year-old ice

17:07.359 --> 17:08.810
can be sourced endlessly from Kunlun.

17:09.220 --> 17:10.890
The purest part

17:11.050 --> 17:12.569
lies beneath the Snow Lotus.

17:14.119 --> 17:15.200
Saintess,

17:15.450 --> 17:16.690
would you like to see it?

17:19.450 --> 17:21.210
If you hadn't mentioned it,

17:21.230 --> 17:23.140
I wouldn't have known.

17:23.310 --> 17:25.270
Kunlun and the Fox Clan have never been on good terms.

17:25.750 --> 17:27.579
Are you really so at ease drinking tea

17:27.609 --> 17:29.010
that I brewed?

17:29.070 --> 17:31.350
You came from afar for peace talks

17:31.370 --> 17:31.970
to bring

17:32.000 --> 17:33.370
tranquility to the countless lives

17:33.390 --> 17:35.020
of both the Fox Clan and Kunlun.

17:35.050 --> 17:36.420
You're such a noble person,

17:36.440 --> 17:37.480
so you would never

17:37.510 --> 17:38.600
engage in despicable deeds.

17:39.280 --> 17:40.870
I've misjudged you with a narrow mind.

17:41.360 --> 17:42.690
Your doubt

17:42.710 --> 17:43.910
is quite understandable.

17:44.590 --> 17:46.190
Just as I too want to ask you—

17:46.210 --> 17:47.950
did you really come here

17:48.010 --> 17:49.770
with no other intention?

17:50.810 --> 17:53.410
Isn't my intention to seek peace

17:53.430 --> 17:55.860
for countless Fox Clan members enough?

17:56.850 --> 17:59.550
I've heard of Saintess Ling Long's heroic qualities for many years,

17:59.860 --> 18:01.030
and seeing you today

18:01.060 --> 18:02.170
I can confirm those words are true.

18:02.190 --> 18:03.910
I have long admired you

18:03.940 --> 18:05.810
and have always wanted to come to Kunlun to see

18:05.830 --> 18:07.700
what Saint Rong Xian of Kunlun

18:07.730 --> 18:09.210
truly looks like.

18:09.920 --> 18:11.230
Now that you've seen me,

18:11.250 --> 18:12.320
what do you think?

18:12.450 --> 18:13.690
Even the stars in the sky

18:13.720 --> 18:15.440
cannot hide your brilliance.

18:26.530 --> 18:27.290
By the way,

18:27.310 --> 18:27.900
I heard that

18:27.930 --> 18:29.500
the old Chief of the Fox Clan is seriously ill.

18:29.770 --> 18:31.260
How is he doing recently?

18:31.450 --> 18:33.370
The old Chief is blessed

18:33.400 --> 18:34.590
and has strong spiritual power.

18:34.900 --> 18:37.140
With the treatment of the Fox Clan's holy healer,

18:37.170 --> 18:38.500
he has fully recovered.

18:38.750 --> 18:40.220
Thank you for your concern.

18:40.540 --> 18:41.410
That's good.

18:47.690 --> 18:50.560
Kunlun is full of suspicions.

18:50.690 --> 18:51.740
The Fox Clan entered the mountain,

18:51.770 --> 18:53.400
but the elders are all avoiding us.

18:53.420 --> 18:55.380
Bei Chen and Mu Jiu also seemed to have disappeared.

18:55.980 --> 18:56.980
But the longer we wait, the more complicated it will become.

18:57.010 --> 18:58.410
We can only give them this one night

18:58.430 --> 18:59.920
to spend together.

18:59.950 --> 19:00.980
Once we get the Snow Lotus,

19:01.000 --> 19:02.840
let's take Ling Long and leave Kunlun as quickly as possible.

19:07.270 --> 19:08.220
The Snow Lotus!

19:08.960 --> 19:09.640
Wait.

19:10.570 --> 19:11.840
Is there a trap?

19:44.340 --> 19:45.100
Let's go!

19:45.280 --> 19:46.560
The Fox Clan is indeed crafty.

19:46.580 --> 19:47.690
They used the peace talks as a cover to steal our treasure.

19:47.720 --> 19:49.160
Fortunately, the Elders have already made preparations.

19:49.180 --> 19:49.740
Today,

19:49.770 --> 19:51.170
you won't be able to go back.

19:51.510 --> 19:52.190
Capture them!

19:52.210 --> 19:52.900
Yes!

20:18.140 --> 20:19.180
Oh no.

20:19.330 --> 20:20.790
Wu and Qi were discovered.

20:22.310 --> 20:24.540
The Elders had already made arrangements around the Snow Lotus.

20:24.560 --> 20:25.670
You won't be able

20:25.700 --> 20:26.720
to save them now.

20:26.750 --> 20:28.420
You knew our plan all along?

20:28.880 --> 20:29.850
Did you come tonight

20:29.880 --> 20:31.280
just to watch me fail?

20:31.300 --> 20:32.090
Ling Long,

20:32.120 --> 20:33.390
you really don't remember me?

20:38.830 --> 20:39.410
Hurry!

20:40.670 --> 20:41.320
Hurry!

20:41.990 --> 20:42.600
Someone is coming.

20:42.620 --> 20:43.380
Come with me.

20:48.110 --> 20:49.720
The old Chief of the Fox Clan is seriously ill.

20:49.740 --> 20:51.690
I know you're here for the Snow Lotus.

20:51.720 --> 20:52.370
Take it.

20:52.390 --> 20:53.250
Leave Kunlun now.

20:53.270 --> 20:54.030
No.

20:54.060 --> 20:55.330
Wu and the others are still inside.

20:55.350 --> 20:56.510
I can't leave.

20:56.540 --> 20:58.190
Leave Wu and those two attendants to me.

20:58.210 --> 21:00.210
I will send them back to the Fox Clan safely.

21:00.240 --> 21:02.340
But since you knew I was lying to you,

21:02.400 --> 21:03.830
why are you still helping me?

21:03.890 --> 21:05.020
Ling Long,

21:05.040 --> 21:07.010
Kunlun is not where we first met.

21:07.130 --> 21:08.310
I've known you

21:08.680 --> 21:09.580
for a long time.

21:11.370 --> 21:12.570
Do you remember

21:12.600 --> 21:13.510
ten years ago,

21:14.200 --> 21:15.570
in Qingling Mountain,

21:15.700 --> 21:17.720
when you saved a severely wounded Eternal?

21:18.320 --> 21:19.430
Ten years ago?

21:21.030 --> 21:22.220
It was you?

21:23.350 --> 21:24.950
At that time, I was ambushed by demons,

21:24.970 --> 21:26.450
severely injured, and fell off a cliff.

21:26.660 --> 21:27.900
My face was covered in wounds.

21:28.730 --> 21:30.290
It's normal that you didn't recognize me.

21:31.400 --> 21:33.680
If you hadn't taken care of me for three days,

21:33.710 --> 21:35.870
I might have died at the bottom of the cliff.

21:35.940 --> 21:37.100
The reason I didn't tell you

21:37.120 --> 21:38.570
when we met again today

21:38.600 --> 21:40.000
wasn't that I wanted to deceive you intentionally.

21:40.090 --> 21:41.090
I just...

21:42.920 --> 21:45.230
just wanted to spend more time with you.

21:46.090 --> 21:48.290
Although Kunlun and the Fox Clan have been enemies for years,

21:48.360 --> 21:50.750
I have always hoped the two clans could reconcile.

21:51.100 --> 21:52.420
The two clans have a deep grudge;

21:52.450 --> 21:54.150
someone has to take the first step.

21:55.330 --> 21:56.160
So,

21:56.330 --> 21:57.320
take the Snow Lotus

21:57.820 --> 21:58.980
to save the old Chief.

22:03.790 --> 22:04.860
But if Kunlun finds out

22:04.890 --> 22:06.050
you helped me,

22:06.070 --> 22:07.520
how will they deal with you?

22:07.550 --> 22:08.520
Don't worry.

22:08.550 --> 22:09.860
I am the Saint after all.

22:09.890 --> 22:10.650
At most,

22:10.670 --> 22:11.840
I'll just get scolded by my master.

22:11.870 --> 22:12.500
I won't die.

22:12.520 --> 22:13.570
I won't forget

22:13.770 --> 22:14.730
your kindness today.

22:15.290 --> 22:16.330
If there's an opportunity in the future,

22:16.360 --> 22:17.630
I'll repay it.

22:35.920 --> 22:37.050
What happened?

22:37.080 --> 22:38.520
Why are we suddenly here?

22:41.830 --> 22:42.700
They...

22:43.290 --> 22:44.710
We were still a step too late.

22:45.060 --> 22:47.570
Emotions in this world are truly unpredictable.

22:47.590 --> 22:50.350
Some feelings may take a thousand or ten thousand years to develop,

22:50.910 --> 22:52.680
while others

22:52.700 --> 22:54.610
might arise in the blink of an eye.

23:00.110 --> 23:01.660
Why is it changing again?

23:01.680 --> 23:03.670
It's Rong Xian's obsession leading us.

23:03.690 --> 23:04.580
Everything in this illusion

23:04.610 --> 23:06.500
changes according to his key memories.

23:06.520 --> 23:07.820
Where will we go?

23:08.260 --> 23:09.090
I don't know.

23:18.850 --> 23:19.740
Qi.

23:20.680 --> 23:22.010
What's wrong with you today?

23:22.040 --> 23:23.670
You've lost five rounds already.

23:23.690 --> 23:25.040
It's...

23:25.120 --> 23:26.490
Sister, don't misunderstand.

23:26.510 --> 23:29.070
He was just too tired last night and didn't rest well,

23:29.100 --> 23:29.860
so he spaced out.

23:31.430 --> 23:32.450
I see.

23:34.890 --> 23:36.530
It's not what you think.

23:36.560 --> 23:37.480
It is.

23:44.980 --> 23:45.790
Last night...

23:45.820 --> 23:47.490
I was too tired, so today I feel a bit weary.

23:47.960 --> 23:48.710
I understand.

23:48.730 --> 23:49.620
You're young,

23:50.040 --> 23:51.040
full of energy.

23:51.060 --> 23:52.080
I can understand.

23:54.710 --> 23:55.380
Here.

23:57.340 --> 23:58.540
You took back your card again.

23:58.980 --> 24:00.390
What do you mean "again"?

24:00.410 --> 24:01.850
Haven't you done it before?

24:01.880 --> 24:02.750
I haven't.

24:02.780 --> 24:03.930
Not taking back cards

24:03.950 --> 24:05.360
is a noble act.

24:05.390 --> 24:06.180
Yes.

24:06.200 --> 24:06.960
You are noble.

24:06.990 --> 24:08.330
Then why don't you cook?

24:08.360 --> 24:09.430
For the past month,

24:09.450 --> 24:10.250
I've been the one cooking at home.

24:10.280 --> 24:12.280
That's because you refused to wash the dishes first.

24:12.300 --> 24:13.890
So now you want to bring up old grievances?

24:13.920 --> 24:15.390
I've been the one doing the laundry.

24:15.880 --> 24:16.990
That was me.

24:17.070 --> 24:18.420
You always forget to collect them.

24:18.440 --> 24:20.090
How can you lie?

24:20.120 --> 24:21.150
Even if I did collect them,

24:21.180 --> 24:22.700
you'd still throw them all over the place,

24:22.720 --> 24:24.040
and I wouldn't be able to find anything!

24:24.070 --> 24:25.620
You, the Saint of Kunlun,

24:25.650 --> 24:26.610
are lazy and don't know life at all.

24:26.630 --> 24:28.190
That's because I have order in my chaos.

24:28.240 --> 24:29.350
When have I ever failed to find something

24:29.350 --> 24:30.140
when you asked me to?

24:30.160 --> 24:31.550
You always forget our anniversaries.

24:31.590 --> 24:33.160
Who has hundreds of anniversaries in a year?

24:33.160 --> 24:34.430
You have secret money.

24:34.460 --> 24:35.350
With a fierce wife,

24:35.400 --> 24:37.350
this is my last line of defense and dignity.

24:38.240 --> 24:40.240
Actually, these are not important.

24:40.450 --> 24:41.170
Shut up!

24:44.170 --> 24:45.220
You don't love me anymore.

24:55.600 --> 24:57.090
What I saw just now

24:57.120 --> 24:59.800
was the Saintess of Fox Clan and the Saint of Kunlun?

24:59.820 --> 25:02.060
You saw an ordinary couple.

25:02.520 --> 25:04.080
They say that marriage is like a tomb.

25:05.150 --> 25:06.820
That makes sense. They didn't deceive me.

25:07.720 --> 25:10.240
This should be the place where Rong Xian and Ling Long

25:10.260 --> 25:12.000
lived in seclusion, which Bei Chen mentioned before—

25:12.030 --> 25:13.100
Carefree Valley.

25:13.120 --> 25:15.120
They've grown so tired of each other already.

25:15.150 --> 25:17.020
It shouldn't be hard to break them up.

25:33.890 --> 25:34.850
Sister,

25:35.000 --> 25:36.590
I really feel for you.

25:36.610 --> 25:38.820
You gave up your position as Saintess for him,

25:38.850 --> 25:39.810
enduring public criticism.

25:40.240 --> 25:41.270
But what about him?

25:41.270 --> 25:42.790
It hasn't been long,

25:42.790 --> 25:44.030
and he's already speaking to you harshly,

25:44.030 --> 25:45.110
with no patience at all.

25:45.110 --> 25:46.270
The Saint of Kunlun,

25:46.270 --> 25:48.030
pure and untainted, the best of his time?

25:48.590 --> 25:50.030
I think men are all bad.

25:50.030 --> 25:51.750
He's not that bad.

25:54.990 --> 25:55.920
Wu,

25:55.950 --> 25:56.850
you're still young.

25:56.870 --> 25:59.310
What you see now is just romance.

25:59.340 --> 26:01.900
But when two people live together for a long time,

26:01.920 --> 26:03.880
it's never just about romance and passion.

26:03.900 --> 26:06.350
In the end, it all comes to a simple life.

26:06.380 --> 26:08.530
Although he's not good at cooking,

26:08.550 --> 26:10.340
he knows I always sleep in,

26:10.370 --> 26:12.470
so he always gets up early to prepare breakfast.

26:12.970 --> 26:15.100
He always puts things everywhere,

26:15.190 --> 26:18.020
but whenever I can't find something,

26:18.150 --> 26:20.070
he always manages to find it for me.

26:20.740 --> 26:21.700
Although he can't remember

26:21.720 --> 26:23.850
all our little anniversaries,

26:23.880 --> 26:24.880
he always prepares

26:24.880 --> 26:26.230
a thoughtful gift for me,

26:26.250 --> 26:27.480
never repeating.

26:27.570 --> 26:28.490
Even if he forgets,

26:28.520 --> 26:29.880
he always makes it up to me.

26:29.900 --> 26:31.270
When you think about it,

26:31.300 --> 26:32.930
all these little things

26:32.950 --> 26:35.520
are the happiness in our ordinary life.

26:36.740 --> 26:37.590
Marriage

26:37.610 --> 26:39.020
should be like this.

26:39.040 --> 26:40.670
Besides,

26:40.700 --> 26:42.460
I've already...

26:50.960 --> 26:51.810
Qi,

26:51.830 --> 26:52.790
did you see that?

26:52.820 --> 26:53.900
Married women

26:53.920 --> 26:54.970
are really scary.

26:55.000 --> 26:56.030
Who has

26:56.030 --> 26:57.160
100 anniversaries in a year?

26:57.180 --> 26:57.740
And after using

26:57.770 --> 26:59.080
any ornament in the house,

26:59.110 --> 27:00.310
it must be put back in its exact place.

27:00.340 --> 27:01.740
If I get it wrong, she scolds me.

27:01.760 --> 27:03.390
She doesn't even let me save any secret money.

27:03.420 --> 27:04.310
Isn't that terrifying?

27:04.330 --> 27:05.280
Terrifying, right?

27:06.680 --> 27:07.630
Yes.

27:07.870 --> 27:09.280
So my advice is,

27:09.300 --> 27:10.580
you should return to Kunlun

27:10.610 --> 27:11.370
and continue to be the Saint.

27:12.540 --> 27:13.860
How can I do that?

27:13.890 --> 27:14.770
For me,

27:14.790 --> 27:15.440
Ling Long left her clan,

27:15.440 --> 27:16.410
abandoned her position as Saintess,

27:16.430 --> 27:17.950
and came with me to live in this secluded place.

27:17.980 --> 27:19.110
How can I abandon her?

27:19.890 --> 27:20.600
Besides,

27:22.140 --> 27:23.790
she often breaks bowls

27:23.910 --> 27:25.550
because she thinks I'm too tired from cooking,

27:25.570 --> 27:26.610
and she breaks them

27:26.640 --> 27:28.070
while fighting with me to do the dishes.

27:28.820 --> 27:31.130
Remembering every single one of our anniversaries

27:31.160 --> 27:32.530
shows how much she cares about me.

27:33.470 --> 27:35.170
Not letting me save secret money

27:35.540 --> 27:37.630
is because she's afraid I'll sneak out to buy alcohol

27:37.970 --> 27:39.720
and get spotted by Kunlun and the Fox Clan.

27:42.060 --> 27:43.340
With such a wife,

27:43.960 --> 27:45.240
I have nothing more to ask for.

27:46.440 --> 27:47.160
No.

27:47.410 --> 27:48.850
I have to coax her now.

28:00.570 --> 28:02.160
I didn't manage to persuade Ling Long.

28:02.180 --> 28:03.150
How about you?

28:03.460 --> 28:04.270
No.

28:05.840 --> 28:07.120
Bei Chen said that

28:07.550 --> 28:09.660
not long after Rong Xian and Ling Long lived in seclusion,

28:09.680 --> 28:11.330
the Fox Clan and Kunlun encountered problems.

28:11.740 --> 28:12.650
Fan Yue,

28:12.680 --> 28:14.330
we don't have much time left.

28:15.100 --> 28:17.040
What do you think of Rong Xian?

28:17.190 --> 28:19.070
He became too talkative after getting married,

28:20.730 --> 28:21.880
but he is also kind,

28:21.900 --> 28:22.620
righteous,

28:22.650 --> 28:23.950
and noble.

28:24.020 --> 28:25.810
And he is deeply devoted to Ling Long.

28:26.320 --> 28:27.560
As you can see,

28:27.580 --> 28:28.630
Ling Long gave up her position

28:28.680 --> 28:30.670
as the Chief of the Fox Clan for Rong Xian.

28:30.860 --> 28:32.950
But why did she suddenly go to wipe out Kunlun?

28:32.980 --> 28:35.210
What happened a thousand years ago

28:35.530 --> 28:37.460
that led them to this point, where one of them must die?

28:56.870 --> 28:58.700
I was wrong.

29:05.220 --> 29:06.850
It's always like this.

29:06.870 --> 29:08.440
You have to argue with me,

29:08.530 --> 29:10.560
and then I have to apologize to you.

29:10.620 --> 29:11.550
Yes, yes.

29:11.570 --> 29:12.770
It's all my fault.

29:14.140 --> 29:15.310
There's something

29:15.340 --> 29:16.410
I want to tell you.

29:16.830 --> 29:17.870
What is it?

29:25.440 --> 29:26.720
It's a letter from Kunlun.

29:31.010 --> 29:32.220
Open it.

29:32.520 --> 29:33.470
Actually,

29:33.490 --> 29:35.680
if Kunlun really wanted to stop us from being together,

29:35.710 --> 29:36.560
they would have found us

29:36.580 --> 29:38.060
long ago during these three years.

29:41.030 --> 29:44.430
[Master is seriously ill and on the verge of death. Return quickly]

29:46.750 --> 29:48.260
What happened?

29:48.280 --> 29:49.270
The letter says

29:50.020 --> 29:51.240
that my master is seriously ill

29:52.130 --> 29:53.390
and nearing the end of his life.

29:55.970 --> 29:57.490
I have to go back to Kunlun.

30:00.400 --> 30:01.240
Don't worry.

30:01.260 --> 30:03.130
I'm just going back to see my master.

30:04.050 --> 30:06.260
The Kunlun Sect Leader has treated you like a master and a father.

30:06.350 --> 30:07.590
You should go back.

30:09.250 --> 30:10.010
By the way,

30:10.060 --> 30:11.650
what did you

30:11.680 --> 30:12.640
want to tell me just now?

30:14.480 --> 30:16.350
I'll tell you when you come back.

30:16.590 --> 30:17.500
Just go.

30:17.520 --> 30:18.470
I'll take care of things at home.

30:46.670 --> 30:47.970
Three years?

30:48.590 --> 30:50.310
Why is it already three years later?

30:52.880 --> 30:54.250
I still haven't finished beating that Bei Chen.

30:55.350 --> 30:56.520
In this realm of resentment,

30:56.970 --> 30:59.450
time changes without any logic at all.

30:59.470 --> 31:01.250
I wonder where those three were sent.

31:04.090 --> 31:05.230
Am I

31:05.450 --> 31:07.310
going to stay in this stupid illusion

31:07.540 --> 31:08.580
for the rest of my life?

31:19.850 --> 31:21.170
Why is he back?

31:33.570 --> 31:34.200
Master.

31:35.220 --> 31:36.900
You've been gone for three years,

31:37.330 --> 31:38.820
and you're finally back.

31:39.510 --> 31:40.400
I'm sorry.

31:40.420 --> 31:41.690
During these three years,

31:41.970 --> 31:44.310
the Eternals and Demons have been fighting incessantly.

31:44.380 --> 31:49.840
[In Harmony with Heaven and Earth]

31:44.640 --> 31:47.400
Kunlun has been guarding the boundary between the two races,

31:47.420 --> 31:48.640
and the responsibility is immense.

31:48.910 --> 31:49.700
Rong Xian,

31:50.490 --> 31:52.490
I don't have much time left,

31:52.520 --> 31:55.250
but Kunlun now has no one capable of bearing such a heavy responsibility.

31:56.280 --> 31:58.120
You are my only disciple

31:58.360 --> 32:00.120
and the Saint of Kunlun.

32:00.850 --> 32:01.680
Only you

32:02.360 --> 32:04.810
can inherit the position of Kunlun Sect Leader.

32:04.830 --> 32:05.790
Master,

32:05.820 --> 32:06.900
the dangers and evil of the world

32:06.920 --> 32:08.170
do not have just one source.

32:08.190 --> 32:09.840
Not all demons are evil and should be eradicated.

32:10.530 --> 32:11.730
Nonsense!

32:11.870 --> 32:13.240
Demons are wreaking havoc in the world.

32:13.260 --> 32:14.570
They should be eradicated.

32:14.600 --> 32:16.080
The Eternals and the demons have been fighting for over a thousand years.

32:16.100 --> 32:17.620
The casualties include not only demons

32:17.650 --> 32:19.340
but also Eternals and Kunlun disciples.

32:19.360 --> 32:20.400
Why don't we stop the war

32:20.430 --> 32:22.020
to prevent the world from being flooded with blood?

32:22.070 --> 32:23.350
Eradicating the demons

32:23.440 --> 32:25.740
and protecting the people is Kunlun's duty.

32:25.770 --> 32:26.690
Rong Xian,

32:26.900 --> 32:27.950
don't forget,

32:28.130 --> 32:29.710
you are the Saint of Kunlun.

32:32.400 --> 32:34.260
I've left Kunlun for a long time,

32:34.510 --> 32:36.310
and I no longer want to get involved in the conflicts between the two races.

32:37.590 --> 32:38.670
As for inheriting the position of the Sect Leader,

32:40.140 --> 32:42.120
I can only let you down.

32:43.920 --> 32:45.000
-Rong Xian!
-Rong Xian!

32:48.320 --> 32:50.450
You don't want to take on the position of the Sect Leader

32:50.470 --> 32:53.170
because you can't let go of that Fox Clan Saintess, right?

33:00.500 --> 33:02.770
It's true that I don't want the slaughter between the Eternals and the demons to continue,

33:03.590 --> 33:05.480
but it's also true that I can't let go of Ling Long.

33:05.720 --> 33:07.200
Ling Long and I

33:07.230 --> 33:08.860
swore to be together for life.

33:09.090 --> 33:10.370
I will never break that promise

33:10.640 --> 33:11.850
and betray her.

33:11.880 --> 33:13.490
Since you can't let go,

33:14.280 --> 33:15.850
I'll make the decision for you.

33:15.880 --> 33:16.550
[In Harmony with Heaven and Earth]

33:19.110 --> 33:20.110
Master,

33:20.130 --> 33:21.540
what are you doing?

33:22.590 --> 33:25.240
Eternals and demons are destined to fight each other to the death.

33:25.270 --> 33:25.990
Rong Xian,

33:26.010 --> 33:28.080
you are the hope of all Kunlun.

33:28.110 --> 33:29.190
I cannot allow you

33:29.200 --> 33:31.000
to abandon your sect

33:31.030 --> 33:32.310
and the Eternal Race

33:32.340 --> 33:33.830
for a Fox Clan demoness.

33:33.850 --> 33:35.610
In order to preserve Kunlun's reputation

33:34.640 --> 33:38.790
[In Harmony with Heaven and Earth]

33:35.640 --> 33:36.990
and thousand-year legacy,

33:37.340 --> 33:39.990
I will transfer all my spiritual power to you

33:40.020 --> 33:43.170
and change all of your memories with that demoness.

33:45.300 --> 33:46.300
Rong Xian,

33:46.330 --> 33:47.440
remember,

33:47.460 --> 33:48.940
your parents and closest kin

33:48.970 --> 33:51.140
were all killed by the Fox Clan.

33:51.170 --> 33:53.740
Three years ago, it was you

33:53.760 --> 33:56.100
who deceived Ling Long into going into seclusion,

33:56.320 --> 33:57.630
all to make

33:57.650 --> 34:01.060
the Fox Clan lose their strongest heir.

33:59.060 --> 34:01.180
[In Harmony with Heaven and Earth]

34:01.090 --> 34:03.920
You have never loved Ling Long.

34:03.370 --> 34:05.690
[In Harmony with Heaven and Earth]

34:03.940 --> 34:06.110
You only have hatred

34:06.140 --> 34:07.430
and murderous intent toward her.

34:08.360 --> 34:10.150
My parents and closest kin

34:10.179 --> 34:12.580
were all killed by the Fox Clan.

34:13.530 --> 34:15.580
I have never loved Ling Long.

34:16.139 --> 34:17.909
The Demon Race deserves to die.

34:18.790 --> 34:20.440
The Fox Clan deserves to die!

34:27.460 --> 34:28.500
Is this

34:28.530 --> 34:30.639
the true reason Rong Xian slaughtered the Fox Clan?

34:31.400 --> 34:32.480
I must hurry back to the Fox Clan

34:32.500 --> 34:33.710
and tell them everything.

34:34.120 --> 34:34.870
Stop!

34:34.900 --> 34:36.310
You were spying outside the Sect Leader's room.

34:36.330 --> 34:36.920
Take him away!

34:37.330 --> 34:38.239
What are you doing?

34:38.280 --> 34:39.239
Let go of me!

34:39.820 --> 34:40.300
Move!

34:50.030 --> 34:50.800
Sister.

34:51.449 --> 34:53.340
I haven't seen Rong Xian all afternoon.

34:53.360 --> 34:54.500
Where did he go?

34:54.530 --> 34:56.170
He went back to Kunlun.

34:56.380 --> 34:58.590
Why did Rong Xian suddenly go back to Kunlun?

35:01.290 --> 35:03.250
Did you two have a fight,

35:03.280 --> 35:04.110
and he

35:04.130 --> 35:05.450
went back to Kunlun out of anger?

35:06.350 --> 35:07.540
Of course not.

35:07.560 --> 35:08.770
The Sect Leader of Kunlun is seriously ill

35:08.800 --> 35:09.950
and summoned him back.

35:14.430 --> 35:15.310
What's wrong?

35:20.840 --> 35:21.890
Wu,

35:22.070 --> 35:23.150
over the past three years,

35:23.180 --> 35:25.240
you've been living in seclusion with me in Carefree Valley.

35:25.420 --> 35:26.460
I know

35:26.490 --> 35:28.430
that you and Qi are in love with each other.

35:29.960 --> 35:31.670
Why did you suddenly bring this up?

35:33.040 --> 35:35.370
I just feel that Qi is gentle,

35:35.390 --> 35:36.820
kind, and upright.

35:36.850 --> 35:37.900
If you choose him,

35:37.930 --> 35:39.040
I will be at ease.

35:39.500 --> 35:41.150
You've always been a free spirit,

35:41.170 --> 35:42.400
not interested in practicing magic.

35:42.980 --> 35:43.750
Now that

35:43.770 --> 35:45.390
you've left the Fox Clan,

35:45.530 --> 35:47.260
just don't go back.

35:47.290 --> 35:47.850
From now on,

35:47.870 --> 35:49.910
stay in Carefree Valley with Qi

35:49.940 --> 35:52.300
and live as a simple, carefree couple.

35:53.120 --> 35:54.280
Sister,

35:54.440 --> 35:55.740
what happened exactly?

35:57.070 --> 35:58.920
I just suddenly feel

35:58.950 --> 36:00.920
that my little Wu has grown up.

36:07.810 --> 36:08.840
Let's take a look!

36:08.860 --> 36:09.830
What happened?

36:09.860 --> 36:11.050
-Get up.
-What happened?

36:11.070 --> 36:12.430
What happened?

36:24.770 --> 36:25.730
Rong Xian?

36:26.720 --> 36:28.720
Aren't you living in seclusion with the Saintess in Carefree Valley?

36:28.740 --> 36:30.290
Why did you suddenly barge into the Fox Clan?

36:30.770 --> 36:32.310
Did something happen to the Saintess?

37:18.200 --> 37:18.840
Saint,

37:18.860 --> 37:19.660
stop!

37:37.980 --> 37:38.910
Why?

37:41.260 --> 37:42.660
Why?

37:44.720 --> 37:46.550
After all this,

37:46.580 --> 37:48.640
haven't you understood?

37:51.030 --> 37:52.790
From the start,

37:52.810 --> 37:54.510
he got close to you intentionally.

37:55.260 --> 37:57.970
You are the Fox Clan's most powerful Saintess.

37:57.990 --> 37:59.700
You were supposed to inherit the position of Chief

37:59.730 --> 38:01.210
and strengthen our Fox Clan,

38:01.890 --> 38:03.050
but he

38:03.650 --> 38:06.130
deceived you into living in seclusion,

38:06.150 --> 38:07.740
keeping you away from the clan.

38:07.770 --> 38:10.160
And while you were gone, he came to Jingyou Mountain

38:10.190 --> 38:12.270
and slaughtered us.

38:12.410 --> 38:13.820
All of this

38:14.670 --> 38:17.420
is a conspiracy of Kunlun!

38:18.190 --> 38:19.660
That's not true.

38:22.260 --> 38:24.240
It's not true, right?

38:24.970 --> 38:26.940
Who would use three years to set up a trap,

38:27.450 --> 38:30.130
spending thousands of days and nights together?

38:31.920 --> 38:34.000
No one would do that.

38:35.060 --> 38:37.020
If I had known you were this stupid,

38:37.820 --> 38:40.040
I wouldn't have gone to all the trouble to scheme for three years.

38:41.110 --> 38:42.590
For the past three years,

38:43.800 --> 38:46.160
every moment I pretended to love you,

38:50.170 --> 38:51.710
I felt

38:53.290 --> 38:55.160
utterly disgusted!

39:06.040 --> 39:07.680
But it's also thanks to you.

39:08.050 --> 39:10.290
If you hadn't trusted me completely,

39:10.420 --> 39:12.780
how would I have known everything about the Fox Clan?

39:12.810 --> 39:14.510
When I was charging up the mountain,

39:14.660 --> 39:16.620
it felt like walking into an unprotected territory.

39:26.170 --> 39:27.250
Miss Ling Long!

39:27.280 --> 39:28.400
Saintess!

39:28.520 --> 39:30.810
Even if these three years were all a lie.

39:31.750 --> 39:34.110
Even if you never loved me.

39:34.710 --> 39:35.630
Rong Xian,

39:36.880 --> 39:39.470
they are all living beings.

39:40.060 --> 39:42.200
How could you bring yourself to do that?

39:42.220 --> 39:44.810
They are just a group of vile demons.

39:48.790 --> 39:49.970
And you.

39:52.360 --> 39:53.690
You're the same.

39:54.830 --> 39:56.020
Vile,

39:56.100 --> 39:57.590
and disgusting.

40:02.620 --> 40:04.620
I am the Saint of an Eternal Sect.

40:05.260 --> 40:07.690
How could I ever fall in love with a demon?

40:10.310 --> 40:12.020
Ridiculous.

40:12.290 --> 40:13.410
There should be an end

40:14.580 --> 40:16.160
between us!

40:23.130 --> 40:24.270
Miss Ling Long!

40:24.290 --> 40:26.190
Saintess!

40:43.040 --> 40:47.320
♫No matter if I'm drunk or not, I just want to be reckless once♫

40:49.440 --> 40:54.900
♫Because love is thrilling♫

40:51.480 --> 40:52.920
Miss Ling Long!

40:52.940 --> 40:54.690
Saintess!

40:55.400 --> 40:59.040
♫If you tear open my heart♫

40:55.940 --> 40:57.750
I have long admired you

40:57.780 --> 40:59.550
and have always wanted to come to Kunlun to see

40:59.840 --> 41:02.150
♫I can hold you a little tighter♫

40:59.850 --> 41:01.750
what Saint Rong Xian of Kunlun

41:01.770 --> 41:03.410
truly looks like.

41:02.600 --> 41:06.910
♫This pain will gradually fade♫

41:09.220 --> 41:13.060
♫Time withers the moonlight♫

41:09.600 --> 41:11.540
But since you knew I was lying to you,

41:11.920 --> 41:13.490
why are you still helping me?

41:13.830 --> 41:16.070
♫All that's left is pitch darkness♫

41:13.970 --> 41:14.930
I won't forget

41:14.960 --> 41:16.130
your kindness today.

41:16.220 --> 41:17.300
If there's an opportunity in the future,

41:16.470 --> 41:18.470
♫I want to tear apart♫

41:17.320 --> 41:18.720
I'll repay it.

41:18.970 --> 41:22.070
♫This sky for you♫

41:21.390 --> 41:22.850
You always forget our anniversaries.

41:22.870 --> 41:24.100
Who has hundreds of anniversaries in a year?

41:22.930 --> 41:25.970
♫A lifetime of guarding everything with you♫

41:24.130 --> 41:25.490
You have secret money.

41:26.270 --> 41:29.740
♫Crossing the abyss to fulfill our vow♫

41:27.740 --> 41:29.770
I'll tell you when you come back.

41:29.790 --> 41:31.010
Just go.

41:29.980 --> 41:33.390
♫I'll leap without a thought for tomorrow♫

41:31.030 --> 41:31.960
I'll take care of things at home.

41:33.660 --> 41:36.260
♫This moment feels like forever♫

41:36.700 --> 41:39.520
♫I've missed too much time in my life♫

41:39.830 --> 41:43.640
♫I'll throw myself into this flame for you♫

41:43.840 --> 41:45.830
♫Even if I'll perish♫

41:45.880 --> 41:48.650
♫At least I can still kiss your face♫

41:48.880 --> 41:52.100
♫Burn out my waning moon♫

41:52.360 --> 42:00.600
♫In exchange for a lifetime of passion♫

41:59.350 --> 42:01.880
Eternals and demons are destined to fight each other to the death.

42:01.880 --> 42:02.920
Why?

42:02.920 --> 42:05.150
All of this is a conspiracy of Kunlun!

42:05.170 --> 42:06.830
You fox demoness!

42:36.410 --> 42:38.270
Long!

42:38.930 --> 42:40.220
Long!

42:40.460 --> 42:45.420
♫What kind of flower would never bear fruit?♫

42:41.070 --> 42:41.990
Long!

42:44.860 --> 42:45.700
Ling Long!

42:46.430 --> 42:47.120
Ling Long!

42:48.580 --> 42:54.210
♫What kind of fruit never sees a flower?♫

42:53.320 --> 42:54.510
I'm sorry.

42:55.010 --> 42:56.140
I didn't mean it.

42:56.870 --> 43:04.300
♫Withstanding the stillness, you are a broken piece of me♫

43:02.360 --> 43:03.540
Our...

43:05.160 --> 43:07.080
child...

43:05.220 --> 43:10.270
♫I am the fruit to your flowers♫

43:16.240 --> 43:19.800
♫Across thousands of miles♫

43:24.570 --> 43:29.260
♫The pain of parting lingers♫

43:27.720 --> 43:28.830
Child?

43:31.030 --> 43:31.950
Child?

43:31.890 --> 43:39.160
♫ I light a lamp with no wick to carry me through the rest of my days♫

43:36.620 --> 43:37.850
What child?

43:40.040 --> 43:41.400
What child?

43:40.230 --> 43:44.900
♫Flowers in the wind, sand in the water♫

43:42.040 --> 43:43.680
Can't you see

43:43.730 --> 43:47.310
that she's already pregnant with your child?

43:47.800 --> 43:50.000
Children conceived

43:47.980 --> 43:53.280
♫What kind of tree never takes root?♫

43:50.020 --> 43:52.110
by an Eternal and a demon

43:52.140 --> 43:55.620
are naturally flawed and hard to carry to term.

43:56.010 --> 44:01.470
♫What kind of roots never turn into trees♫

43:56.150 --> 44:00.110
She has expended a great deal of her own spiritual power to sustain the baby.

44:00.140 --> 44:01.370
Otherwise,

44:02.600 --> 44:06.900
she wouldn't have so easily died under your sword!

44:04.510 --> 44:11.630
♫ To break the roots of love, to look at the past and seal one's heart ♫

44:07.610 --> 44:08.940
Rong Xian,

44:09.260 --> 44:11.780
what you've done

44:11.800 --> 44:15.510
is unforgivable!

44:11.980 --> 44:16.890
♫I'm your wanderer♫

44:17.290 --> 44:18.410
It was me.

44:19.930 --> 44:21.060
It was me.

44:20.000 --> 44:24.310
♫The flowers flew away♫

44:22.400 --> 44:24.010
It was me

44:24.280 --> 44:26.240
who killed our child.

44:26.880 --> 44:29.050
It was me who killed Ling Long.

44:27.700 --> 44:31.840
♫My tears are streaming down like rain♫

44:29.720 --> 44:31.160
Why?

44:33.380 --> 44:36.070
Why did you do this to me?

44:35.790 --> 44:43.060
♫Light my heart's lamp, cast away attachments, and ask the world♫

44:39.000 --> 44:40.360
Why?

44:44.620 --> 44:50.350
♫On the vast sea, you and I♫
